{"tid":202293,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"模擬樂園 起過山車intensity rating 太高","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T03:08:54.000Z","uid":66701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b69cc93830ac44122c4fb416a520e3c78b089a","tid":202293,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/193348_499488125d634d948a73f1f5a301ff9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F15%2F193348_499488125d634d948a73f1f5a301ff9d.jpg&h=0169297b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢關要過山車既excitement 過6.6，要自己起<br />\n<br />\n但控制到excitement 就控制唔到intensity rating太高，g force 又高<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求點起過山車解救方法"},{"pid":"7c6cce9252ba820aa13656014cb46f9fc87f0407","tid":202293,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"巴打win幾 我一直都玩唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開就係負色片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d618428af5466c4eb1d3aee322f8324a40ed7d0e","tid":202293,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:43:37.000Z","msg":"軌道有唔同款例如細彎,大彎,S形, loop之類根據唔同種類既過山車而有唔同 我經驗上覺得你過山車個design入面用得愈多唔同款既軌道 excitement rating愈高<br />\n<br />\n另外想降低intensity可以test run睇下邊段既vertical G, horizontal G太高, 例如直落既可以改design做斜軌轉住落<br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999, 利申我都係卡左係呢關無動力過"},{"pid":"754db5094fd7e9e50b9bf29901c5e78641b38038","tid":202293,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:44:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打win幾 我一直都玩唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開就係負色片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無睇錯原po玩緊mobile版"},{"pid":"ff3003ce521aad3d858247a70c603ec7a4916f3d","tid":202293,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打win幾 我一直都玩唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開就係負色片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n手機版來<br />\n<br />\nI know 負色片,試過<br />\n<br />\n你重新裝過喇"},{"pid":"57c699a03519652d955ebe799a1a0da4c684aa6e","tid":202293,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>軌道有唔同款例如細彎,大彎,S形, loop之類根據唔同種類既過山車而有唔同 我經驗上覺得你過山車個design入面用得愈多唔同款既軌道 excitement rating愈高<br />\n<br />\n另外想降低intensity可以test run睇下邊段既vertical G, horizontal G太高, 例如直落既可以改design做斜軌轉住落<br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999, 利申我都係卡左係呢關無動力過</blockquote><br />\n當然如果你想出少少cheat 可以係過山車軌附近狂起裝飾 boost個excitement rating"},{"pid":"41ea757caf93cb74c015ab321619027fd7c610b4","tid":202293,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:50:30.000Z","msg":"上面巴打好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係卡係呢關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8164718c39271a3c078dfb0b53a093eb66bd097","tid":202293,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"一<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/195115_491fc714c166af949166b422935d3654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F15%2F195115_491fc714c166af949166b422935d3654.jpg&h=49ca0284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要玩晒藍色先開 紫色俾人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f393b79bfa7719f8584cc31c6bf2a7ad79772e","tid":202293,"uid":48510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"執左去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 渣ga 整到咁刺激想嚇死啲人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}